            <title><![CDATA[Battlefield 6 has brought back a community-favourite dog tag for all the high fliers out there]]></title>
            <link>https://www.eurogamer.net/battlefield-6-has-brought-back-a-community-favourite-dog-tag-for-all-the-high-fliers-out-there</link>
